{"tid":2064958,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"經濟不景 「五毛」變「兩毛」","createTime":"2020-06-15T07:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T08:39:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a79ac5f645a39e6b0fd7939917a237a6fd345e88","tid":2064958,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:37:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200615/32646RWRILLLC24HNTR7QJ4XHY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200615%2F32646RWRILLLC24HNTR7QJ4XHY%2F&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8qjPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=ce0f3599\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200615%2F32646RWRILLLC24HNTR7QJ4XHY%2F&h=fdd77b36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200615/32646RWRILLLC24HNTR7QJ4XHY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n經濟不景 「五毛」變「兩毛」<br />\n<br />\n受中美貿易戰和武漢肺炎疫情衝擊，總理李克強明確要求「各級政府必須真正過緊日子」，全面壓縮支出之際，「五毛黨」網軍亦遭波及。據中國招聘「評論兼職」酬勞顯示，由原先每帖0.5元（人民幣，下同）減至0.2元，有網民笑謔：「現在經濟不景氣，真正的五毛黨降低到兩毛黨了！」時事評論員劉夢熊向本報表示，無論是「五毛黨」還是「二毛黨」，利益驅使下，只要有甜頭都會把良知拋諸腦後，基於一種無知和偏見「亂咁吠」，淪為謊言治國的工具。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GC3JDPZ6IL4UPXOCV7NHL4D3OY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGC3JDPZ6IL4UPXOCV7NHL4D3OY.gif&h=3a803296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經濟不景，五毛工資跟着下調。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉夢熊嘲見利亂吠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n微博「頭條稿子」近日招聘「評論兼職」，工作內容是「根據每一條文案進行評論」，並要求應徵者「擅於多角色、多角度、多種風格去進行評論」，還需要先寫出10條評論供考核。而酬勞則為「中度20字」評論0.2元、「深度40字」0.3元，附圖則再加0.1元。惟今年4月，有網軍分享收入清單顯示，每則評論為0.7元，網民一度揚言今後可改稱「七毛」。<br />\n<br />\n對於網軍酬勞大減，..............................................「雁過拔毛」是慣例，「五毛變兩毛」也是官場腐敗的必然反映。<br />\n<br />\n「五毛黨」為中國網絡城牆下的產物，.......................................可以獲得0.5元報酬。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者/新浪微博"},{"pid":"6d3753c1f5f7b3d71e9b28d99d09c62f0eccb939","tid":2064958,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:41:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd14d925ec31901780c2df396bc3dfb36f5bc9e1","tid":2064958,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:56:41.000Z","msg":"得2毛點生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796df0403ed3d780de0e420f3078aadf2b77f03a","tid":2064958,"uid":300006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"全民小康，每人每日要25000個留言<br />\n連登要開多d post 比佢地留言"},{"pid":"45fdce0b2e2ef65d02c33c76c9e069ddfef31e28","tid":2064958,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得而家D五毛咁撚低質<br />\n之前風生水起叔打幾多字幾有心機"}]}